data.title: What's my wooden / metal airplane propeller worth?
data.meta_description: Here you will find a collection of both wooden and metal airplane propellers and blades that have sold on eBay and other sites. Prices and Date Sold.
data.meta_site_name: Aviation Art  | Airplane Furniture | Pilot Gifts - Plane Pieces Inc
data.text:
Here you will find a collection of both wooden and metal airplane propellers and blades that have sold on eBay and other sites. Manufacturers will include Sensenich, McCauley, Hartzell, Curtiss Reed, Fairey Reed, Hamilton Standard, Paragon, Fahlin, Banks Maxwell, Flottorp, GB Lewis, Gardner, Stone, Supreme, Univair, Thomas Morse Scout, Liberty, Sterling Burgess, Lang, Starr Piano, Jacuzzi, Hegy and many more.

If you can't find what you are looking for shoot us an email with several photos of your propeller(s) to planepieces@gmail.com and we will be happy to help identify and value your propeller(s) as best we can.

*** We will not respond to calls or voicemails. Email Only and please be patient as we receive 10-20 requests a week ***
